The paper discusses audio/visual recognition and retrieval applications in the context of Internet-of-Things (IoT) oriented services, which suggests a strong connection to the cs.IOT sub-category. The paper also focuses on optimizing the coupling between device energy consumption and cloud infrastructure billing, which could fall under the cs.DC and cs.SY sub-categories. The use of image descriptors and image similarity detection suggests a connection to the cs.CV and cs.MM sub-categories.
